[link: /commands/docs/stor_create.md] ``stor create``
Create a table in the in-memory sqlite database.
built-in
[link: /commands/docs/stor_delete.md] ``stor delete``
Delete a table or specified rows in the in-memory sqlite database.
built-in
[link: /commands/docs/stor_export.md] ``stor export``
Export the in-memory sqlite database to a sqlite database file.
built-in
[link: /commands/docs/stor_import.md] ``stor import``
Import a sqlite database file into the in-memory sqlite database.
built-in
[link: /commands/docs/stor_insert.md] ``stor insert``
Insert information into a specified table in the in-memory sqlite database.
built-in
[link: /commands/docs/stor_open.md] ``stor open``
Opens the in-memory sqlite database.
built-in
[link: /commands/docs/stor_reset.md] ``stor reset``
Reset the in-memory database by dropping all tables.
built-in
[link: /commands/docs/stor_update.md] ``stor update``
Update information in a specified table in the in-memory sqlite database.
built-in
